title: Erich von Stroheim's THE WEDDING MARCH (1928)

sources.title: ErichVonStroheimsTheWeddingMarch1928
sources.description: Co-starring Zasu Pitts and Fay Wray whose career was pricesely launched by this film. Apparently, the sequel "The Honneymoon" was definitively lost during the 1950s. more info on http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0019558/ and http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Wedding_March_(film)
